cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.AI 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with speech recognition and language-independent automatic speech recognition. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with acoustic landmarks in speech. Additionally, it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a multi-task learning approach using neural networks. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with developing a strategy for language-independent automatic speech recognition.
